                     <interp inst="t18600402-376-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="breakingPeace"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18600402-376-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="wounding"></interp>for feloniously wounding <persName id="t18600402-name-370" type="victimName">
