                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi> 
                     <hi rend="italic">of unlawfully wounding.</hi>
                  </rs>
                  <hi rend="italic"> The prosecutor stated that tlie prisoner had assaulted and threatened him on several occasions, but that he had no desire that he should be punished; all he wished was to be protected from violence.</hi>
               </p>
